trans-unit.source: Provides an external process for running add-ins out-of-process from the host application.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en ekstern prosess for å kjøre tillegg-prosesseksterne fra vertsprogrammet.

trans-unit.source: To activate an add-in in an external process, pass an AddInProcess object to the appropriate <xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInToken.Activate%60%601%28System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess%2CSystem.Security.PermissionSet%29?displayProperty=fullName> method overload.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil aktivere et tillegg i en ekstern prosess, kan du sende et objekt som AddInProcess til de riktige <xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInToken.Activate%60%601%28System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess%2CSystem.Security.PermissionSet%29?displayProperty=fullName>metoden overbelastning.</xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInToken.Activate%60%601%28System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess%2CSystem.Security.PermissionSet%29?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The executable that runs the add-in is obtained from one of two files installed with the .NET Framework under the Windows directory.
trans-unit.target: Den kjørbare filen som kjøres tillegget hentes fra en av to filer som er installert med .NET Framework under Windows-mappen.

trans-unit.source: By default, the executable that matches the bits-per-word of the host application is used.
trans-unit.target: Den kjørbare filen som samsvarer med bits-per-ordet for applikasjonen som vert brukes som standard.

trans-unit.source: If the host is a 64-bit process, AddInProcess.exe is run; otherwise, AddInProcess32.exe is run.
trans-unit.target: Hvis verten er en 64-biters prosess, kjører AddInProcess.exe; Ellers kjører AddInProcess32.exe.

trans-unit.source: To specify the way the executable is selected, use the <xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess.%23ctor%28System.AddIn.Hosting.Platform%29> constructor to create the AddInProcess object.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil angi hvordan den kjørbare filen er valgt, kan du bruke den <xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess.%23ctor%28System.AddIn.Hosting.Platform%29>konstruktøren for å opprette AddInProcess-objektet.</xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess.%23ctor%28System.AddIn.Hosting.Platform%29>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: This constructor has the same effect as using the <xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess.%23ctor%28System.AddIn.Hosting.Platform%29> constructor with the <xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.Platform?displayProperty=fullName> flag, to specify that the process that runs the add-in will have the same bits-per-word as the host process.
trans-unit.target: Denne konstruktøren virker på samme måte som når du bruker den <xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess.%23ctor%28System.AddIn.Hosting.Platform%29>konstruktør med den <xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.Platform?displayProperty=fullName>Flagg for å angi at prosessen som kjører tillegget skal ha samme bits-per-ord som vertsprosessen.</xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.Platform?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess.%23ctor%28System.AddIn.Hosting.Platform%29>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess"></xref> class, specifying the bits-per-word of the process in which the add-in runs.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess"> </xref> klasse, angir bits-per-ordet av prosessen som tillegget kjører.

trans-unit.source: The following table shows how `platform` affects the bits-per-word of the process on different operating systems: ||32-bit operating system|64-bit operating system| |-|------------------------------|------------------------------| |Host|32-bit|Same as the host process| |AnyCPU|32-bit|64-bit| |X86|32-bit|32-bit| |X64|Exception is thrown|64-bit|
trans-unit.target: Tabellen nedenfor viser hvordan `platform` påvirker bits-per-ordet av prosessen på ulike operativsystemer: ||&32;-biters operativsystem |&64;-biters operativsystem | |-|------------------------------|------------------------------| | Vert |&32;-biters | Samme som vertsprosessen | | AnyCPU |&32;-biters |&64;-biters | | X86 |&32;-biters |&32;-biters | | X64 | Unntak |&64;-biters |

trans-unit.source: A value that specifies the bits-per-word of the process that runs the add-in.
trans-unit.target: En verdi som angir bits-per-ordet av prosessen som kjører tilleggsprogrammet.

trans-unit.source: The registry entry for the path to the executable (AddInProcess.exe or AddInProcess32.exe) is missing.
trans-unit.target: Registeroppføringen for banen til den kjørbare filen (AddInProcess.exe eller AddInProcess32.exe) mangler.

trans-unit.source: -or- The executable is missing.
trans-unit.target: - eller - mangler den kjørbare filen.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the current <xref href="System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess"></xref> object represents the host application process.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om gjeldende <xref href="System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess"> </xref> objektet representerer vertsprosessen for programmet.

trans-unit.source: If the value of this property is `true`, the add-in is running in-process with the host application.
trans-unit.target: Hvis verdien for denne egenskapen `true`, tillegget er kjører under en prosess med vertsprogrammet.

trans-unit.source: In that case, using the <xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess.Start%2A> or <xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess.Shutdown%2A> method throws an <xref:System.InvalidOperationException>.
trans-unit.target: I dette tilfellet bruker <xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess.Start%2A>eller <xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess.Shutdown%2A>metoden oppstår en <xref:System.InvalidOperationException>.</xref:System.InvalidOperationException> </xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess.Shutdown%2A> </xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess.Start%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The <xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInEnvironment.Process%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property returns an <xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess> object that represents the host application process if the add-in is running in-process.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Den <xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInEnvironment.Process%2A?displayProperty=fullName>returnerer en <xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess>objektet som representerer programmet vertsprosessen Hvis tillegget kjører kjørende.</xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess> </xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInEnvironment.Process%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the <xref href="System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess"></xref> object corresponds to the current process; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis den <xref href="System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess"> </xref> objektet samsvarer med gjeldende behandle; ellers, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that indicates whether to keep the external process alive.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om du vil beholde den eksterne prosessen aktiv.

trans-unit.source: Set this property to `false` to aggressively shut down the external process after the last add-in inside the process has been shut down.
trans-unit.target: Sett denne egenskapen til `false` støttealternativer avsluttes ekstern prosess etter siste tillegget i prosessen ble avsluttet.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the external process should be kept alive; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis den eksterne prosessen skal vært åpen; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the bits-per-word of the process in which the out-of-process add-in is run.
trans-unit.target: Henter bits-per-ordet av prosessen som tillegget utenfor prosessen kjører.

trans-unit.source: The bits-per-word is set when the <xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess> object is initialized, and cannot be changed.
trans-unit.target: Bits-per-ordet angis når den <xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess>objektet er initialisert og kan ikke endres.</xref:System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess>

trans-unit.source: The bits-per-word of the process that runs the add-in.
trans-unit.target: Bits-per-ordet av prosessen som kjører tilleggsprogrammet.

trans-unit.source: Gets the process ID of the external process.
trans-unit.target: Henter prosess-IDen for den eksterne prosessen.

trans-unit.source: Use this property for debugging.
trans-unit.target: Bruk denne egenskapen for feilsøking.

trans-unit.source: The process ID, or -1 if the external process has not started.
trans-unit.target: Prosess-IDen eller -1 hvis den eksterne prosessen ikke startet.

trans-unit.source: Forcibly shuts down the external process.
trans-unit.target: Avslutter ekstern prosess ved tvang.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the external process was running and is successfully shut down; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> if there is no active process associated with the <xref href="System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis den eksterne prosessen ble kjører og er avsluttet; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> Hvis det er ikke aktiv prosess knyttet til den <xref href="System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The add-in is running in-process with the host application.
trans-unit.target: Tillegget er kjører under en prosess med vertsprogrammet.

trans-unit.source: Starting and stopping the process is allowed only for external processes, not for the host process.
trans-unit.target: Starte og stoppe prosessen er bare tillatt for eksterne prosesser ikke for vertsprosessen.

trans-unit.target: Forekommer når prosessen som representerer den <xref href="System.AddIn.Hosting.AddInProcess"> </xref> objektet skal bli avsluttet.

trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis prosessen startet; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> Hvis prosessen kjører allerede.

trans-unit.source: The add-in is running in-process with the host application.
trans-unit.target: Tillegget er kjører under en prosess med vertsprogrammet.

trans-unit.source: Starting and stopping the process is allowed only for external processes, not for the host process.
trans-unit.target: Starte og stoppe prosessen er bare tillatt for eksterne prosesser ikke for vertsprosessen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the number of seconds to allow for the process to start.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir antall sekunder å tillate starte prosessen.

trans-unit.source: The default value is 10 seconds.
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien er 10 sekunder.

trans-unit.source: This property is usually used during debugging, to increase the startup time for the process that runs the out-of-process add-in.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen brukes vanligvis under feilsøking, for å øke tiden startet prosessen som kjører tillegget utenfor prosessen.

trans-unit.target: Antall sekunder å tillate oppstart.

trans-unit.target: Prosessen kjører allerede.
